WEBVTT

00:07.724 --> 00:16.586
♪♪

00:16.586 --> 00:25.310
♪♪

00:25.310 --> 00:29.482
[Bird chirping]

00:36.344 --> 00:39.137
-[Breathing heavily]

00:42.793 --> 00:45.379
[Chain jingling]

00:45.379 --> 00:48.000
[Panting]

01:03.310 --> 01:06.275
[Shouts indistinctly]

01:06.275 --> 01:09.793
-[Shrieking loudly]

01:09.793 --> 01:12.413
-[Grunting]

01:17.724 --> 01:20.344
[Hissing stops]

01:22.793 --> 01:30.137
♪♪

01:30.137 --> 01:37.655
♪♪

01:37.655 --> 01:40.068
[Birds cawing]

01:40.068 --> 01:47.413
♪♪

01:47.413 --> 01:54.620
♪♪

01:54.620 --> 02:02.000
♪♪

02:03.965 --> 02:06.517
-[Speaks indistinctly]

02:06.517 --> 02:08.137
Look.

02:08.137 --> 02:09.896
[People moaning]
-[Speaks indistinctly]

02:09.896 --> 02:12.517
[Chuckles]

02:19.655 --> 02:22.241
-The least you could've done
was phone.

02:24.172 --> 02:26.379
You need to start
helping yourself.

02:26.379 --> 02:30.758
-I was sick.
-Yeah. What's that? Calpol.

02:30.758 --> 02:33.344
-They don't want me
working there anyway.

02:33.344 --> 02:35.586
-Did someone say something?

02:35.586 --> 02:37.655
I can't do anything
unless you tell me.

02:37.655 --> 02:39.000
-It was nothing.

02:39.000 --> 02:40.827
-Fine. Let's go.
Leave the bottle.

02:40.827 --> 02:42.896
-You know, you shouldn't even
be on this property.

02:42.896 --> 02:44.172
-Just sit and drink your beer.

02:44.172 --> 02:46.344
-Are you deaf?
-Come on. Last time.

02:46.344 --> 02:48.448
-I'm talking to you, you cunt.
Hey.

02:48.448 --> 02:50.241
-Come on. This is the last time.
-Hey!

02:50.241 --> 02:53.103
Here.
-[Gasps]

02:53.103 --> 02:54.965
-Don't. Baggo, stop.

02:54.965 --> 02:57.137
-Baggo --
-Get the fuck --

02:57.137 --> 02:58.793
[Grunts] Fuck!

02:58.793 --> 03:00.344
Get!

03:00.344 --> 03:02.172
Aah!
-Get off her!

03:02.172 --> 03:03.931
♪♪

03:03.931 --> 03:06.344
-Aah!

03:06.344 --> 03:07.586
-[Breathes heavily]

03:07.586 --> 03:10.965
-She started it,
you useless, fat pig.

03:10.965 --> 03:12.758
Wanker.

03:12.758 --> 03:13.862
-You alright to drive?

03:13.862 --> 03:15.862
-Ah, looks worse than it is.

03:15.862 --> 03:17.482
-You should go to the hospital.

03:17.482 --> 03:19.655
-Got to take him home.
-'Course you do.

03:19.655 --> 03:21.551
-We better go. See ya.

03:26.655 --> 03:28.172
Let's go.

03:31.000 --> 03:32.551
Get in.
-Cathy.

03:32.551 --> 03:33.931
-What?

03:33.931 --> 03:35.724
-Are you seeing anyone?

03:39.068 --> 03:41.275
-[Sighs]

03:41.275 --> 03:44.068
[Bird chirping]

03:45.310 --> 03:47.758
Said he loved me.

03:47.758 --> 03:49.310
-Did you give him
the boundaries chart?

03:49.310 --> 03:53.241
-[Scoffs] He doesn't know
what a boundary is.

03:53.241 --> 03:55.620
-You need to nip that
in the bud.

03:55.620 --> 03:58.482
There you go.
-Julie gave me the Laidlaw case.

03:58.482 --> 04:00.172
Seriously, Bill, you need to
sort this out right now.

04:00.172 --> 04:01.965
I'm not going anywhere near --
-Whoa, whoa, whoa. Slow down.

04:01.965 --> 04:03.379
Julie what?

04:03.379 --> 04:04.655
-Gave me Bloody Mary.

04:04.655 --> 04:06.172
-I don't want that name
being used.

04:06.172 --> 04:09.689
-Who's this?

04:09.689 --> 04:11.137
-Mary Laidlaw.

04:11.137 --> 04:13.793
She just finished
a life term in North View.

04:13.793 --> 04:15.034
-Bill, I won't do it.

04:15.034 --> 04:16.482
There's no way
I'm going up there.

04:16.482 --> 04:19.137
-I can take it.
-You sure?

04:19.137 --> 04:21.206
-[Sighs] It's fine.
I'll have a read tonight.

04:21.206 --> 04:25.034
-Cathy.
-Ah, you're a lifesaver.

04:25.034 --> 04:27.413
You'll need to put a tag
on her today.

04:30.068 --> 04:33.241
-I thought you had Luke tonight.
-Yeah.

04:42.137 --> 04:44.862
-Were you here in '91?

04:44.862 --> 04:47.137
-I was just starting out.

04:47.137 --> 04:49.172
-What's with the nickname?

04:49.172 --> 04:50.620
-Media shit.

04:50.620 --> 04:53.758
♪♪

04:53.758 --> 04:57.413
She killed her husband
with an ax

04:57.413 --> 05:00.862
after he beat her half to death
and set her on fire.

05:00.862 --> 05:03.551
-Jesus.

05:03.551 --> 05:06.931
-Left for dead up there
in the moss.

05:06.931 --> 05:09.103
It was a miracle she survived.

05:09.103 --> 05:11.758
He'd caught her
with this young fella.

05:11.758 --> 05:13.310
I never knew his name.

05:13.310 --> 05:17.275
He used to wander the roads
in this strange getup.

05:17.275 --> 05:20.862
Jim strung them up over a tree
so deep in the moss

05:20.862 --> 05:23.310
it took days to find them.

05:23.310 --> 05:27.896
That's when they found
all the other...stuff.

05:27.896 --> 05:32.172
It's all anyone
talked about for years.

05:32.172 --> 05:34.413
I like to think we've moved on.

05:34.413 --> 05:37.137
♪♪

05:38.137 --> 05:40.344
-What are you doing up here?
-Nothing.

05:40.344 --> 05:42.241
-You know
it's private property.

05:42.241 --> 05:44.275
-We've come to see the witch.

05:44.275 --> 05:45.827
-You better not be here
when I get back.

05:45.827 --> 05:48.310
-Maybe she's a witch and all.
-[Laughs]

05:48.310 --> 05:50.551
-Go home
before I call your parents.

05:50.551 --> 05:51.758
Go on.

05:55.310 --> 05:58.172
-She fed her husband
to his dogs.

06:00.655 --> 06:08.586
♪♪

06:08.586 --> 06:16.379
♪♪

06:16.379 --> 06:20.172
[Indistinct whispering]

06:20.172 --> 06:30.137
♪♪

06:30.137 --> 06:33.000
[Engine shut off]

06:33.000 --> 06:34.758
Brilliant.

06:35.689 --> 06:38.310
[Sighs]

06:42.517 --> 06:48.931
♪♪

06:48.931 --> 06:50.655
Mrs. Laidlaw.

06:50.655 --> 06:59.482
♪♪

06:59.482 --> 07:03.758
Mrs. Laidlaw, it's Cathy Madden.
I'm your supervising officer.

07:03.758 --> 07:05.586
♪♪

07:05.586 --> 07:08.793
Can you open the door, please?

07:08.793 --> 07:10.655
I tried phoning ahead,
but your --

07:10.655 --> 07:12.068
-Line's dead.

07:12.068 --> 07:15.862
♪♪

07:15.862 --> 07:18.413
Where's the other one?

07:18.413 --> 07:19.275
-Who?

07:19.275 --> 07:21.551
-Other woman.

07:21.551 --> 07:24.310
Came up to North View
last month.

07:24.310 --> 07:27.344
-Mrs. Toner. She's gone.

07:27.344 --> 07:29.000
You got me now.

07:29.000 --> 07:33.034
♪♪

07:33.034 --> 07:34.931
-Better come in, then.

07:34.931 --> 07:37.172
♪♪

07:37.172 --> 07:39.413
You can bring that with you.

07:39.413 --> 07:49.103
♪♪

07:49.103 --> 07:59.000
♪♪

07:59.000 --> 08:08.862
♪♪

08:08.862 --> 08:11.448
-[Sighs]

08:11.448 --> 08:15.724
♪♪

08:15.724 --> 08:16.793
I'm really sorry.

08:16.793 --> 08:20.034
The report passed this
as suitable.

08:20.034 --> 08:22.620
I'll contact human resources,
see what they can do.

08:22.620 --> 08:25.034
-Human resources.

08:25.034 --> 08:26.137
-Have you got heating?

08:26.137 --> 08:28.034
-Plenty of wood outside.

08:28.034 --> 08:30.965
♪♪

08:30.965 --> 08:32.689
-I brought you a few things.

08:32.689 --> 08:36.034
♪♪

08:36.034 --> 08:37.965
Oh, there's no need.

08:37.965 --> 08:40.862
♪♪

08:40.862 --> 08:42.344
-Water, then.

08:59.034 --> 09:01.241
-Ah.

09:13.517 --> 09:21.172
♪♪

09:21.172 --> 09:23.758
[Sighs]

09:23.758 --> 09:27.379
♪♪

09:32.241 --> 09:34.655
-You didn't come
to bring me biscuits.

09:36.310 --> 09:39.206
-I have to fit you
with a monitoring tag.

09:41.068 --> 09:43.068
Stays on six months.

09:43.068 --> 09:44.862
Then we review.

09:44.862 --> 09:46.103
[Sighs]

09:46.103 --> 09:49.724
There's notes
in the folder there.

09:49.724 --> 09:51.482
-Help yourself.

09:59.965 --> 10:08.586
♪♪

10:08.586 --> 10:17.034
♪♪

10:17.034 --> 10:18.965
You've got cold hands.

10:18.965 --> 10:22.344
♪♪

10:22.344 --> 10:24.172
-Don't try and take it off.

10:24.172 --> 10:29.137
-I knew a man with hands
nice and cold like that.

10:29.137 --> 10:33.275
-And don't go off your property
without prior permission.

10:33.275 --> 10:35.896
You'll need to get
your phone sorted out.

10:35.896 --> 10:37.103
I can get you credit.

10:37.103 --> 10:39.655
-He took me walking on the moss.

10:39.655 --> 10:40.896
♪♪

10:40.896 --> 10:42.827
-Put his hands on me.

10:42.827 --> 10:44.482
♪♪

10:44.482 --> 10:48.448
The moment he came inside me,
I knew it'd be a boy.

10:48.448 --> 10:54.862
♪♪

10:54.862 --> 10:56.655
You got kids?

10:56.655 --> 10:59.310
-I don't talk about
my personal life.

10:59.310 --> 11:02.758
-I can see you
with a little boy.

11:02.758 --> 11:04.931
They took mine.

11:04.931 --> 11:06.482
Put him in a home.

11:06.482 --> 11:09.931
♪♪

11:09.931 --> 11:11.241
-Have a read of that.

11:11.241 --> 11:12.862
You'll find everything you need
in there.

11:12.862 --> 11:16.275
-No mother should have
a stranger bring up her child.

11:16.275 --> 11:18.172
That's not right.

11:18.172 --> 11:20.068
♪♪

11:20.068 --> 11:22.000
[Speaks indistinctly]

11:22.000 --> 11:29.275
♪♪

11:29.275 --> 11:33.344
-Your first official contact's
on Friday.

11:33.344 --> 11:35.586
-I sent him a letter
every week.

11:35.586 --> 11:39.655
♪♪

11:39.655 --> 11:41.724
11:00 at my office.

11:41.724 --> 11:50.310
♪♪

11:50.310 --> 11:53.620
-Wasn't my husband
on the moss.

11:53.620 --> 11:56.965
♪♪

11:56.965 --> 11:58.689
-I'll see you Friday.

11:58.689 --> 12:06.034
♪♪

12:06.034 --> 12:08.620
[Breathing heavily]

12:08.620 --> 12:14.068
♪♪

12:14.068 --> 12:16.448
-Luke?

12:16.517 --> 12:17.793
Luke?

12:20.482 --> 12:22.172
Luke?

12:25.275 --> 12:28.137
-Do I have to?

12:28.137 --> 12:30.137
-Yeah, you do.

12:30.137 --> 12:32.137
Come on.

12:36.896 --> 12:38.586
-Don't say anything.

12:38.586 --> 12:40.551
-Wasn't gonna.

12:40.551 --> 12:42.103
-Hi, there.

12:42.103 --> 12:43.379
-Hi.

12:47.517 --> 12:49.931
-Hello, Cathy.
-Hi, Grace.

12:49.931 --> 12:52.620
-Hey, go and get your bag.
There's a good boy.

12:52.620 --> 12:54.896
-Go.

12:54.896 --> 12:57.620
-Come in.
We stand on the doorstep?

13:04.137 --> 13:05.379
Take a seat.

13:05.379 --> 13:07.103
-Oh, it's grand.
I wanna get him home.

13:07.103 --> 13:09.689
-[Chuckles]

13:09.689 --> 13:10.655
-You're looking well.

13:10.655 --> 13:13.241
-Honestly? No.
I'm like a whale.

13:13.241 --> 13:15.103
I keep bumping Jason
every time I roll over.

13:15.103 --> 13:17.068
[Chuckles]

13:17.068 --> 13:19.000
His medicine's all packed.

13:19.000 --> 13:20.344
Have you gotten palm cups?

13:20.344 --> 13:21.689
-On his bedroom shelf, yeah.

13:21.689 --> 13:24.275
-Right.

13:24.275 --> 13:26.034
They work you such long hours.

13:26.034 --> 13:28.241
-Last-minute thing.
Landed a new release on me.

13:28.241 --> 13:30.275
-Mary Laidlaw?

13:30.275 --> 13:32.793
A lot of people
been waiting on her getting out.

13:32.793 --> 13:34.965
-Of course.

13:34.965 --> 13:36.241
-I guess
you had to be born here.

13:36.241 --> 13:38.517
-[Chuckles]
-Right.

13:38.517 --> 13:41.655
-Used to tell stories about her
when I was a wee 'un.

13:41.655 --> 13:44.482
Bloody Mary would get us
if we were bad,

13:44.482 --> 13:46.827
take us out to the moss,
chop us up --

13:46.827 --> 13:49.448
-Jason. [Chuckles]

13:53.344 --> 13:54.965
-You sure you're okay?

13:54.965 --> 13:56.655
-Yeah. Just tired.

13:56.655 --> 13:58.000
-We could hold on to Luke
if you want.

13:58.000 --> 13:59.344
-No.

13:59.344 --> 14:00.758
-I could send you home
with something,

14:00.758 --> 14:03.000
a lasagna or crumble --

14:03.000 --> 14:04.758
-Dinner's already sorted.

14:06.000 --> 14:07.344
[Sighs]

14:07.344 --> 14:09.275
Thanks, though.

14:19.620 --> 14:21.275
-See that?

14:21.275 --> 14:22.827
The witch put that there.

14:22.827 --> 14:24.344
-She didn't.

14:27.827 --> 14:29.862
[Bird squawks, wings flap]

14:29.862 --> 14:32.827
-Who's there?

14:32.827 --> 14:34.551
-You're not scaring us!

14:34.551 --> 14:43.413
♪♪

14:44.896 --> 14:47.448
-Can we have witch's pasta?

14:47.448 --> 14:49.448
-What's witch's pasta?

14:49.448 --> 14:52.655
-Grace makes it with pasta.
It's from Italy.

14:52.655 --> 14:56.000
It's Grace--
-Is that right?

14:56.000 --> 14:58.103
I'll get some for next time.

15:02.793 --> 15:05.758
-Is it true you put people
in prison?

15:05.758 --> 15:08.172
Like Daddy?

15:08.172 --> 15:11.862
-Uh, I help them
when they come out.

15:11.862 --> 15:13.896
-Why do you wanna do that?

15:13.896 --> 15:16.137
They're bad people.

15:22.241 --> 15:26.172
You need to do it softer,
like she does.

15:32.448 --> 15:35.137
-[Panting]

15:35.137 --> 15:36.862
Leon!

15:36.862 --> 15:39.068
♪♪

15:39.068 --> 15:41.551
Leon! Leon!

15:41.551 --> 15:43.965
[Gasping]

15:43.965 --> 15:53.413
♪♪

15:53.413 --> 16:02.689
♪♪

16:02.689 --> 16:05.103
-[Inhales deeply]

16:05.103 --> 16:14.034
♪♪

16:14.034 --> 16:22.931
♪♪

16:22.931 --> 16:26.724
[People screaming]

16:26.724 --> 16:32.620
♪♪

16:32.620 --> 16:35.275
-Mommy!
-[Gasps]

16:35.275 --> 16:38.206
-[Breathing rapidly]
I want Mommy!

16:38.206 --> 16:40.034
-Okay, just break it up.
Good lad.

16:40.034 --> 16:41.379
-[Coughing]

16:41.379 --> 16:43.275
-There you go. Good boy.

16:43.275 --> 16:45.862
-[Panting]
-Okay.

16:45.862 --> 16:48.137
You're okay. Shh.

16:48.137 --> 16:50.551
Okay.

16:50.551 --> 16:52.758
Oh, you frightened
the life out of me.

16:52.758 --> 16:54.034
-Who's that?

16:54.034 --> 16:56.931
-Uh, no one.
Someone I'm working with.

16:56.931 --> 16:59.275
-Can I stay up with you?

16:59.275 --> 17:00.655
-You're okay now.

17:00.655 --> 17:01.862
-Please?

17:01.862 --> 17:03.586
-Come on. Back to bed.

17:03.586 --> 17:05.517
Come.

17:05.517 --> 17:09.517
[Machine whirring softly]
-[Breathing raspily]

17:18.310 --> 17:21.103
[Lock clicks]

17:23.172 --> 17:25.793
[Cellphone vibrating]

17:27.586 --> 17:28.793
[Cellphone clicks]

17:28.793 --> 17:31.586
-Hello?
-Sergeant, we've had a report

17:31.586 --> 17:33.137
that the McGrath kids
are missing.

17:33.137 --> 17:35.103
-Are they sure?
Have they run 'round?

17:35.103 --> 17:37.793
-They checked with everyone.
I know you're off duty, but --

17:37.793 --> 17:39.724
-Oh, ain't that right?

17:39.724 --> 17:41.379
Did they say where?

17:41.379 --> 17:44.000
-They were last seen
going into the moss.

17:44.000 --> 17:46.310
-Have Massey meet me...

17:46.310 --> 17:48.137
I'll take a run
past the farm.

17:48.137 --> 17:54.137
♪♪

17:54.137 --> 17:56.517
[Knocking on door]
Mrs. Laidlaw?

17:56.517 --> 18:02.517
♪♪

18:02.517 --> 18:08.379
♪♪

18:08.379 --> 18:12.068
[Knocks on window]

18:12.068 --> 18:13.655
I can see you.

18:30.068 --> 18:31.896
We've got
two children missing.

18:31.896 --> 18:34.965
We had a report they were
hanging 'round here earlier.

18:34.965 --> 18:39.758
A boy of 12,
a girl, age 10.

18:39.758 --> 18:41.034
♪♪

18:41.034 --> 18:43.206
You seen them?

18:43.206 --> 18:45.448
Nobody's been up here
disturbing you?

18:45.448 --> 18:47.551
♪♪

18:47.551 --> 18:50.689
-Just your ex.

18:50.689 --> 18:53.241
Put a tag on me.

18:53.241 --> 18:55.655
-Do you mind if I have
a quick look 'round?

18:55.655 --> 18:58.206
♪♪

18:58.206 --> 19:00.068
-Go ahead.

19:00.068 --> 19:07.068
♪♪

19:07.068 --> 19:14.068
♪♪

19:14.068 --> 19:15.172
-Have you got no lights?

19:15.172 --> 19:16.896
-Waiting to be connected.

19:16.896 --> 19:25.586
♪♪

19:25.586 --> 19:34.068
♪♪

19:34.068 --> 19:42.758
♪♪

19:42.758 --> 19:51.448
♪♪

19:51.448 --> 19:59.965
♪♪

19:59.965 --> 20:08.620
♪♪

20:08.620 --> 20:17.137
♪♪

20:17.137 --> 20:18.689
-Is it just you here?

20:18.689 --> 20:21.827
-Mm-hmm.

20:21.827 --> 20:23.000
-That your car out there?

20:23.000 --> 20:24.551
-Aye.

20:29.655 --> 20:32.241
-I don't smoke.

20:32.241 --> 20:34.724
-Not with a baby on the way.

20:34.724 --> 20:37.241
♪♪

20:37.241 --> 20:39.000
-I won't tell.

20:39.000 --> 20:47.034
♪♪

20:47.034 --> 20:55.103
♪♪

20:55.103 --> 20:57.689
[Lighter clicks]

20:57.689 --> 21:06.896
♪♪

21:06.896 --> 21:16.103
♪♪

21:16.103 --> 21:25.517
♪♪

21:25.517 --> 21:34.724
♪♪

21:34.724 --> 21:43.931
♪♪

21:43.931 --> 21:46.551
[Police radio chatter]

21:50.379 --> 21:52.896
-Leon!
-Leon!

21:52.896 --> 21:54.448
-Jennifer!

21:54.517 --> 21:56.758
-Jennifer!

21:59.655 --> 22:01.413
-Leon!

22:05.586 --> 22:07.344
-Jennifer!

22:09.896 --> 22:13.000
-Laidlaw place isn't far.

22:13.000 --> 22:14.275
-She walks on a stick.

22:14.275 --> 22:16.241
-I've got...here.

22:16.241 --> 22:18.689
Doesn't stop him
from being an evil fucker.

22:20.931 --> 22:24.034
She comes back.
Two kids vanish.

22:24.034 --> 22:26.758
-A day out of prison.

22:26.758 --> 22:31.241
-What they got up to up here
wasn't fun and games.

22:31.241 --> 22:33.413
It was sick.

22:33.413 --> 22:35.586
-I read all about it.

22:35.586 --> 22:36.827
-Did ya?

22:36.827 --> 22:38.586
Well, I sawit.

22:38.586 --> 22:41.034
There's a reason
for the stories.

22:41.034 --> 22:44.379
[Dog barking]

22:44.379 --> 22:46.586
-Excuse me. Excuse me.

22:46.586 --> 22:52.000
♪♪

22:52.000 --> 22:57.620
♪♪

22:58.896 --> 23:00.275
-She knew about Luke?

23:00.275 --> 23:02.931
-Uh, it was just a guess.

23:02.931 --> 23:05.620
-Oh, my God.

23:05.620 --> 23:08.724
I'm so glad she's yours.

23:08.724 --> 23:10.000
What?

23:10.000 --> 23:11.793
I have enough nutjobs.

23:11.793 --> 23:14.586
You know Jerry Finnan
drinks his own piss?

23:17.379 --> 23:20.206
-She was pregnant
when she went inside.

23:20.206 --> 23:21.724
Put him in care.

23:21.724 --> 23:23.793
-Some people
shouldn't have kids.

23:23.793 --> 23:25.620
It's not in them.

23:25.620 --> 23:28.241
[Cellphone vibrates]

23:30.620 --> 23:32.344
-Shit.

23:32.344 --> 23:35.724
Client keeps sending me texts.

23:35.724 --> 23:38.379
[Cellphone vibrates]
Fucking hell.

23:39.310 --> 23:41.275
[Cellphone clicks]

23:41.275 --> 23:43.586
Mary Laidlaw just
went off property.

23:48.758 --> 23:51.379
-[Exhales sharply]

23:55.551 --> 23:58.206
Finish off
and then drive up, okay?

24:01.793 --> 24:04.413
[Sighs]

24:08.034 --> 24:10.724
♪♪

24:10.724 --> 24:12.448
Luke?

24:12.448 --> 24:18.724
♪♪

24:18.724 --> 24:25.000
♪♪

24:25.000 --> 24:26.344
-[Shouts indistinctly]
-Oh.

24:26.344 --> 24:28.241
[Indistinct talking]

24:28.241 --> 24:30.172
[Both chuckle]

24:30.172 --> 24:32.103
Don't do that again.

24:37.862 --> 24:40.482
[Engine shuts off]

24:42.896 --> 24:44.655
-Mary?

24:50.862 --> 24:53.275
What do you think you're doing?

24:53.275 --> 24:55.172
You're breaking the terms
of your license.

24:55.172 --> 24:59.034
-I wanted to see
the old places.

24:59.034 --> 25:03.034
My daddy used to drive me
down here for Friday sweets.

25:03.034 --> 25:04.896
-Whose car is it?

25:04.896 --> 25:06.655
-My daddy's.

25:06.655 --> 25:09.103
Officer found it.

25:09.103 --> 25:12.620
Your ex. Big fella.

25:12.620 --> 25:14.379
Good-looking.

25:14.379 --> 25:17.413
-Let's go.
We'll sort your car out later.

25:21.137 --> 25:29.586
♪♪

25:29.586 --> 25:38.034
♪♪

25:40.586 --> 25:42.344
-Sorry.

25:46.172 --> 25:48.137
-This is your one chance.

25:48.137 --> 25:50.655
You don't get another.

25:50.655 --> 25:53.206
I'll see you Friday.

25:53.206 --> 25:57.344
-You do a good job, Cathy.

25:57.344 --> 25:59.275
Helping people.

26:02.793 --> 26:05.172
Is it what you wanted
for yourself?

26:05.172 --> 26:08.724
♪♪

26:08.724 --> 26:10.586
-Leon!

26:10.586 --> 26:12.413
Jennifer!

26:14.862 --> 26:19.551
♪♪

26:19.551 --> 26:21.310
Leon!

26:21.310 --> 26:23.103
Jennifer!
[Dog barks]

26:23.103 --> 26:26.655
♪♪

26:26.655 --> 26:29.068
[Dog barking]

26:29.068 --> 26:38.000
♪♪

26:38.000 --> 26:46.931
♪♪

26:46.931 --> 26:55.862
♪♪

26:55.862 --> 27:04.793
♪♪

27:04.793 --> 27:07.034
-You can't go in there.

27:07.034 --> 27:08.965
It's not the kids.

27:08.965 --> 27:11.827
-[Sighs]

27:11.896 --> 27:15.379
[Sighs]

27:15.379 --> 27:17.413
-Fella called Shawn Duggan.

27:17.413 --> 27:19.275
Lifted him a few times.

27:20.724 --> 27:22.000
-[Sighs] It's not them.

27:22.000 --> 27:23.620
-You get this whole area
roped off.

27:23.620 --> 27:25.344
I'll call Dr. Walsh.

27:25.344 --> 27:27.931
-[Breathing shakily]

27:27.931 --> 27:29.137
♪♪

27:29.137 --> 27:31.448
-[Crying] Mum.

27:31.448 --> 27:35.103
♪♪

27:35.103 --> 27:37.413
-I know we all wanna find
these kids,

27:37.413 --> 27:38.931
but very soon
it's gonna get dark,

27:38.931 --> 27:40.413
it's gonna get cold,

27:40.413 --> 27:42.586
and if we stay out here,
we're putting ourselves at risk.

27:42.586 --> 27:46.931
6:00 here tomorrow morning
for those of you who can.

27:46.931 --> 27:49.827
Thanks for today.

27:49.827 --> 27:53.103
Go home.
Get some sleep.

28:05.793 --> 28:08.827
-Did you tell Mary Laidlaw
we used to be married?

28:08.827 --> 28:10.000
-Why would I?

28:10.000 --> 28:13.241
-But you spoke to her?
-Yeah.

28:13.241 --> 28:15.551
She said you went up
to put a tag on her.

28:15.551 --> 28:17.965
That was it.

28:17.965 --> 28:20.068
Stay away from her.

28:20.068 --> 28:22.172
-It's my job.

28:25.206 --> 28:27.034
-Elder.

28:27.034 --> 28:28.896
It was in with the body.

28:28.896 --> 28:30.655
Same as on her door.

28:30.655 --> 28:32.103
-There's loads of it
'round here.

28:32.103 --> 28:34.344
-It didn't grow like this.

28:34.344 --> 28:36.620
Someone made that.
It's what these people do.

28:36.620 --> 28:38.344
-[Scoffs]
You sound like Massey.

28:38.344 --> 28:40.034
-Well, you just don't
want to see it, do you?

28:40.034 --> 28:43.482
-You said it yourself.
It's stories to frighten kids.

28:46.724 --> 28:48.896
-Two kids are missing.

28:48.896 --> 28:50.172
♪♪

28:50.172 --> 28:52.758
[Car door opens, closes]

28:52.758 --> 29:01.103
♪♪

29:01.103 --> 29:09.586
♪♪

29:09.586 --> 29:17.931
♪♪

29:17.931 --> 29:26.413
♪♪

29:26.413 --> 29:34.758
♪♪

29:34.758 --> 29:37.379
[Lighter clicks]

29:44.827 --> 29:47.448
[Candle holder clinks]

29:55.862 --> 29:58.862
-[Breathes deeply]

29:58.862 --> 30:01.482
[Cellphone vibrating]

30:07.689 --> 30:08.827
What's up?

30:08.827 --> 30:11.517
-It's Luke.

30:11.517 --> 30:12.517
-Hi, there.

30:12.517 --> 30:15.068
-Daddy said I should call you.

30:15.068 --> 30:17.206
We can all go somewhere
next week

30:17.206 --> 30:18.827
if you're not working.

30:18.827 --> 30:20.482
-Alright, good boy. Now,
say good night to your mum.

30:20.482 --> 30:22.034
-I've got to go back
to bed now.

30:22.034 --> 30:23.758
Bye.

30:23.758 --> 30:25.655
-Good night.

30:25.655 --> 30:28.241
Thanks.

30:28.241 --> 30:31.275
-Pretty shitty day.
Better tomorrow.

30:31.275 --> 30:33.793
'Night.
-Good night, Jason.

30:39.896 --> 30:42.103
[Cellphone clicks]

30:42.103 --> 30:44.724
[Cellphone vibrates]

30:49.586 --> 30:52.172
[Cellphone clicks]

30:52.172 --> 30:55.793
♪♪

30:56.689 --> 30:59.482
[Indistinct talking
in distance]

31:01.517 --> 31:04.137
[Lighter clicks]

31:08.655 --> 31:11.275
[Dog barking in distance]

31:15.068 --> 31:16.689
-Hey, Cathy, what are you --

31:16.689 --> 31:19.689
-I get one more text from you,
you are going back inside.

31:19.689 --> 31:21.068
Do you understand?

31:21.068 --> 31:30.344
♪♪

31:30.344 --> 31:32.931
-[Whispering indistinctly]

31:32.931 --> 31:40.586
♪♪

31:40.586 --> 31:48.068
♪♪

31:48.068 --> 31:50.655
-[Crying]

31:50.655 --> 32:00.103
♪♪

32:00.103 --> 32:02.689
[Gasps]

32:02.689 --> 32:12.103
♪♪

32:12.103 --> 32:21.655
♪♪

32:21.655 --> 32:31.068
♪♪

32:31.068 --> 32:33.724
-You don't want to get sick,
do you?

32:33.724 --> 32:36.482
♪♪

32:36.482 --> 32:38.965
You don't.

32:38.965 --> 32:40.793
There's a good girl.

32:40.793 --> 32:49.206
♪♪

32:49.206 --> 32:57.827
♪♪

32:57.827 --> 33:00.103
See?

33:00.103 --> 33:02.103
Sweet like honey.

33:02.103 --> 33:04.689
-[Crying]

33:04.689 --> 33:12.965
♪♪

33:12.965 --> 33:21.206
♪♪

33:21.206 --> 33:29.655
♪♪

33:29.655 --> 33:31.586
-The girl first.

33:31.586 --> 33:36.724
♪♪

33:36.724 --> 33:38.586
-Leon!

33:40.689 --> 33:42.413
Jennifer!

33:50.965 --> 33:53.103
Leon!

33:54.827 --> 33:56.586
Jennifer!

34:12.000 --> 34:14.620
[Line ringing]

34:16.724 --> 34:18.862
-Cathy,
I'll call you back.

34:18.862 --> 34:20.793
-I'm in the woods
about a mile from where

34:20.793 --> 34:22.344
you found Shawn Duggan.

34:22.344 --> 34:24.344
There are all these holes --
-I can't talk right now.

34:24.344 --> 34:25.655
-Remember how his hands
were covered in mud?

34:25.655 --> 34:27.551
-Cathy...

34:27.551 --> 34:29.517
we found them.

34:29.517 --> 34:37.137
♪♪

34:37.137 --> 34:44.965
♪♪

34:44.965 --> 34:52.758
♪♪

34:52.758 --> 35:00.586
♪♪

35:00.586 --> 35:02.137
All this...

35:02.137 --> 35:05.068
shit...

35:05.068 --> 35:07.965
stays between us.

35:07.965 --> 35:09.896
We don't want it
getting out.

35:09.896 --> 35:18.551
♪♪

35:18.551 --> 35:27.000
♪♪

35:27.000 --> 35:35.655
♪♪

35:35.655 --> 35:38.068
-[Sniffles]

35:38.068 --> 35:43.137
♪♪

35:43.137 --> 35:48.379
♪♪

35:52.000 --> 35:54.310
-Hello, Tina.

35:57.551 --> 35:59.344
Nathan.

36:03.206 --> 36:06.310
I-I'll just pop these
down here.

36:06.310 --> 36:08.689
I'm so sorry for your loss.

36:08.689 --> 36:12.206
Is -- Is there --
Is there anything I can d-do?

36:12.206 --> 36:13.620
Did you put in
a good word for her?

36:13.620 --> 36:15.793
-For, uh...?
-Bloody Mary.

36:15.793 --> 36:18.241
-No, I-I -- I di-- didn't have
anything to do with that.

36:18.241 --> 36:21.172
-You got the gall
to set foot in my house?

36:23.448 --> 36:25.379
-It's horrendous what has
happened to your family.

36:25.379 --> 36:27.586
-Get out.
-It's nothing to do with me.

36:27.586 --> 36:28.724
-Get out!

36:28.724 --> 36:33.103
♪♪

36:33.103 --> 36:35.689
[Door closes]

36:35.689 --> 36:42.931
♪♪

36:42.931 --> 36:50.137
♪♪

36:50.137 --> 36:51.965
[Car door closes]

36:51.965 --> 36:54.896
-Have you been in?

36:54.896 --> 36:57.241
-[Sighs]
Just now, yeah.

36:57.241 --> 37:00.068
Without their wee ones...

37:00.068 --> 37:01.344
how can they bear it?

37:01.344 --> 37:03.310
-I don't know if they can.

37:05.620 --> 37:07.413
-Head home.

37:10.965 --> 37:13.586
[Engine starts]

37:18.724 --> 37:21.655
[Engine starts]

37:21.655 --> 37:24.137
[Tires squeal]

37:24.137 --> 37:31.517
♪♪

37:41.103 --> 37:43.517
-There she is. Up back.

37:46.827 --> 37:48.896
[Clank]
-[Screams]

37:48.896 --> 37:51.517
[Siren wails]

37:53.482 --> 37:56.103
[Grunting]

37:56.103 --> 37:58.206
-You people need to leave.

37:59.793 --> 38:02.310
I'm not messing around.
Go on, get out.

38:03.103 --> 38:05.379
[Grunting continues]

38:05.379 --> 38:08.482
He's gonna lose his leg
if he doesn't get to hospital.

38:08.482 --> 38:10.241
-[Groaning]

38:10.241 --> 38:12.655
-I'll charge the lot of ya.
Do you hear me?

38:17.724 --> 38:20.862
Go home, Nathan.

38:20.862 --> 38:22.206
Be with your wife.

38:22.206 --> 38:24.689
It's your own wife
you should be looking at.

38:24.689 --> 38:28.137
Your ex cozying up
with that bitch.

38:32.689 --> 38:34.689
-Do as he says, Nathan.

38:34.689 --> 38:36.103
Go home.

38:36.827 --> 38:39.448
-[Breathing heavily]

38:50.724 --> 38:53.344
-[Sighs]

38:54.310 --> 38:57.551
-She put traps out.
She knew they were coming.

38:57.551 --> 38:58.758
-It's her land.

38:58.758 --> 39:00.310
-What, that makes it okay?

39:00.310 --> 39:03.103
-No, but, Jason,
she's up here by herself,

39:03.103 --> 39:05.551
and this town thinks
she's the fucking devil.

39:05.551 --> 39:08.965
They could've killed her.
-Well, maybe they should have.

39:08.965 --> 39:10.310
-You don't mean that.

39:10.310 --> 39:13.310
-Don't I? Have half a mind
to be with them.

39:16.206 --> 39:19.655
When we get through this,

39:19.655 --> 39:23.068
Grace wants to invite you
over to the house.

39:26.482 --> 39:30.344
Luke's started
calling her "Mommy."

39:30.344 --> 39:31.517
-I know.

39:31.517 --> 39:34.000
-I told him
you'll always be his Mommy.

39:34.000 --> 39:38.000
It's just, you know,
he sees her every day, and --

39:38.000 --> 39:40.655
-Jason, let's go.

39:40.655 --> 39:43.758
-You better go.
I'm gonna go talk to Mary.

39:43.758 --> 39:45.724
-Why do you bother?

39:45.724 --> 39:47.068
They're all lowlifes.

39:47.068 --> 39:50.379
They all end up the same way,
back in North View.

39:50.379 --> 39:52.448
-Not myclients.

39:59.931 --> 40:02.275
Kids can be cruel.

40:02.275 --> 40:04.310
-So they say.

40:08.413 --> 40:11.965
-You know, they were spotted
'round here, those two wee ones.

40:11.965 --> 40:13.689
-Aye.

40:16.103 --> 40:19.034
-Who do you think took them?

40:19.034 --> 40:21.551
-How should I know?

40:21.551 --> 40:23.379
-I'm trying to help you, Mary.

40:23.379 --> 40:25.655
Can you not see
how it looks?

40:25.655 --> 40:28.275
[Lighter clicks]

40:30.482 --> 40:33.000
-Why do you stay in this town?

40:33.000 --> 40:35.482
You could go anywhere.

40:35.482 --> 40:38.103
-My son's here.
-Take him with you.

40:40.793 --> 40:43.793
♪♪

40:43.793 --> 40:45.655
-What is all this?

40:45.655 --> 40:47.344
-Things I found.

40:49.034 --> 40:57.068
♪♪

40:57.068 --> 41:05.137
♪♪

41:05.137 --> 41:07.413
It's yours if you want it.

41:07.413 --> 41:09.793
♪♪

41:09.793 --> 41:12.103
It's up to you.

41:12.103 --> 41:19.655
♪♪

41:19.655 --> 41:27.241
♪♪

41:32.827 --> 41:36.655
♪♪

41:36.655 --> 41:39.068
-[Groaning]

41:39.068 --> 41:45.586
♪♪

41:45.586 --> 41:48.103
-Do you think
he'd have stayed

41:48.103 --> 41:50.517
if you'd given him
another child?

41:50.517 --> 41:54.827
♪♪

41:54.827 --> 41:57.689
If your insides
weren't all messed up?

41:57.689 --> 42:00.413
♪♪

42:00.413 --> 42:03.344
What sort of mother were you,

42:03.344 --> 42:07.655
lying in bed,
crying all day,

42:07.655 --> 42:10.517
thinking of ways
to kill your baby?

42:10.517 --> 42:11.689
♪♪

42:11.689 --> 42:13.413
-Fuck you.

42:13.413 --> 42:16.206
♪♪

42:16.206 --> 42:18.862
-They didn't suffer.

42:18.862 --> 42:20.551
It was quick.

42:20.551 --> 42:27.379
♪♪

42:27.379 --> 42:32.724
30 years in this skin.

42:32.724 --> 42:35.379
♪♪

42:35.379 --> 42:39.137
Goes all the way down.

42:39.137 --> 42:41.965
-[Breathing shakily]

42:41.965 --> 42:43.862
-Thomas.

42:43.862 --> 42:49.482
♪♪

42:49.482 --> 42:51.896
-[Gasping]

42:51.896 --> 42:54.310
♪♪

42:54.310 --> 42:55.896
[Gasping continues]

42:55.896 --> 42:58.482
[Screams, grunting]

42:58.482 --> 43:06.103
♪♪

43:06.103 --> 43:13.931
♪♪

43:13.931 --> 43:16.517
[Chain jingling]

43:16.517 --> 43:23.103
♪♪

43:23.103 --> 43:25.689
[Panting]

43:25.689 --> 43:27.068
♪♪

43:27.068 --> 43:29.655
[Clank]
[Screams]

43:29.655 --> 43:32.068
[Crying]

43:32.068 --> 43:40.206
♪♪

43:40.206 --> 43:42.793
[Grunting]

43:42.793 --> 43:50.241
♪♪

43:50.241 --> 43:52.827
[Groaning]

43:52.827 --> 43:55.758
♪♪

43:55.758 --> 43:58.206
-You've opened up a vein.

43:58.206 --> 43:59.586
Do as I say.

43:59.586 --> 44:01.655
We'll do what we can
to help ya.

44:01.655 --> 44:04.068
-[Crying]

44:04.068 --> 44:10.862
♪♪

44:10.862 --> 44:17.689
♪♪

44:17.689 --> 44:20.103
[Grunting]

44:20.103 --> 44:28.896
♪♪

44:28.896 --> 44:31.000
-[Sighs]

44:31.000 --> 44:33.586
[Whispering indistinctly]

44:33.586 --> 44:34.862
♪♪

44:34.862 --> 44:37.448
-[Groaning]

44:37.448 --> 44:39.724
♪♪

44:39.724 --> 44:42.137
-[Inhales deeply]

44:42.137 --> 44:48.206
♪♪

44:48.206 --> 44:50.793
-[Groaning]

44:50.793 --> 44:53.551
♪♪

44:53.551 --> 44:55.379
-Do you see?

44:55.379 --> 44:58.793
Remember how Luke screamed
when he came into the world?

44:58.793 --> 45:00.655
So does the mandrake.

45:00.655 --> 45:01.931
♪♪

45:01.931 --> 45:06.275
Looks like a man
because his father was a man.

45:06.275 --> 45:08.862
His mother is the earth.

45:08.862 --> 45:11.448
-[Grunts]

45:11.448 --> 45:12.689
♪♪

45:12.689 --> 45:15.103
-It can't hurt you

45:15.103 --> 45:16.793
if you can't hear it.

45:16.793 --> 45:19.206
-[Breathing heavily]

45:19.206 --> 45:24.413
♪♪

45:24.413 --> 45:27.137
-Be quick,
or you'll bleed to death.

45:27.137 --> 45:29.724
-[Panting]

45:29.724 --> 45:36.758
♪♪

45:36.758 --> 45:39.172
[Grunting]

45:39.172 --> 45:47.068
♪♪

45:47.068 --> 45:54.965
♪♪

45:54.965 --> 46:02.862
♪♪

46:02.862 --> 46:05.448
[Grunting continues]

46:05.448 --> 46:11.896
♪♪

46:11.896 --> 46:18.344
♪♪

46:18.344 --> 46:20.931
[Grunting continues]

46:20.931 --> 46:28.206
♪♪

46:28.206 --> 46:35.689
♪♪

46:35.689 --> 46:38.068
[Breathing heavily]

46:38.068 --> 46:40.620
♪♪

46:40.620 --> 46:43.034
-[Shrieking loudly]

46:43.034 --> 46:50.862
♪♪

46:50.862 --> 46:53.275
[Shrieking stops]

46:53.275 --> 46:55.862
-[Breathing heavily]

46:55.862 --> 46:58.206
♪♪

46:58.206 --> 47:00.793
[Chain jingling]

47:00.793 --> 47:09.896
♪♪

47:09.896 --> 47:19.206
♪♪

48:06.689 --> 48:08.758
-Put her in.

48:08.758 --> 48:15.586
♪♪

48:15.586 --> 48:18.206
-[Gasping]

48:22.310 --> 48:25.103
[Yells, crying]

48:28.103 --> 48:30.724
[Screaming]

48:38.793 --> 48:39.965
♪♪

48:39.965 --> 48:42.068
-Alright.

48:42.068 --> 48:44.655
-[Groans, crying]

48:44.655 --> 48:46.000
♪♪

48:46.000 --> 48:48.586
Aah! [Crying]

48:48.586 --> 48:53.827
♪♪

48:53.827 --> 48:56.413
[Breathing heavily]

48:56.413 --> 48:59.482
♪♪

48:59.482 --> 49:03.310
-[Humming]

49:19.620 --> 49:22.034
[Cellphone clicks]

49:22.034 --> 49:24.655
[Humming continues]

49:28.931 --> 49:37.689
♪♪

49:37.689 --> 49:46.448
♪♪

49:46.448 --> 49:55.034
♪♪

